### What's the issue you encountered?

Pattern editor highlighting drops variables that are declared by a Template with a bit shift as argument

<img width="257" height="239" alt="Image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/66689b4e-dd2a-44c6-8258-ac86067d8815" />

### How can the issue be reproduced?

Example:
```rust
// Data: 50 69 54 45 53 54 00

struct Test1<auto n> {
    u8 value;
    u8 data[n];
};
struct Test2 {
    u8 flag;
    Test1<(flag >> 4)> test1;
    u8 access = test1.value; // red
};

Test2 test2 @ 0;

```

